  "clean_html": "html\n<div><div><div><div><a href=\"/school/harvardx\"><img alt=\"HarvardX: CS50's Introduction to Computer Science\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-discovery.edx-cdn.org%2Forganization%2Flogos%2F44022f13-20df-4666-9111-cede3e5dc5b6-2cc39992c67a.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\" title=\"HarvardX: CS50's Introduction to Computer Science\"/></a><span>HarvardX verified</span></div><h1>HarvardX: CS50's Introduction to Computer Science</h1><p>An introduction to the intellectual enterprises of computer science and the art of programming.</p></div><div><div><div>Next course starts Jun 25</div><div>Ends Dec 31</div></div><div><span>7 336 144</span><span>learners enrolled</span></div></div></div><div><div><h2>Backed by academic excellence and industry recognition</h2><div><div><span>School-certified</span><span>Earn a verified certificate from Harvard University.</span></div><div><span>ACE-approved</span><span>Recommended for college credit by the American Council on Education.</span></div><div><span>Industry-recognized</span><span>Certificates are accepted by top employers worldwide.</span></div></div><div><h3>Grow these skills</h3><div><a href=\"/search?skills.skill=Algorithms\"><div>Algorithms</div></a><a href=\"/search?skills.skill=C+(Programming+Language)\"><div>C (Programming Language)</div></a><a href=\"/search?skills.skill=Cascading+Style+Sheets+(CSS)\"><div>Cascading Style Sheets (CSS)</div></a><a href=\"/search?skills.skill=Computer+Science\"><div>Computer Science</div></a><a href=\"/search?skills.skill=Cryptography\"><div>Cryptography</div></a><a href=\"/search?skills.skill=Data+Structures\"><div>Data Structures</div></a><a href=\"/search?skills.skill=Finance\"><div>Finance</div></a><a href=\"/search?skills.skill=Forensic+Sciences\"><div>Forensic Sciences</div></a><a href=\"/search?skills.skill=HyperText+Markup+Language+(HTML)\"><div>HyperText Markup Language (HTML)</div></a><a href=\"/search?skills.skill=JavaScript+(Programming+Language)\"><div